The paper deals with deep neural networks and their quantization for computer vision applications, which are topics that are typically covered in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and robotics (cs.AR). However, since the focus of the paper is on the optimization of the quantization process using reinforcement learning, we can assume that the paper is more likely to be classified under cs.LG and cs.CV, which are the sub-categories that deal with optimization and computer vision, respectively.
